{"tid":2131850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"髮型屋開放給打工仔食飯   負責人:「讓港人食啖安樂茶飯」","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T06:45:34.000Z","uid":192075,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d79569a263eab480d52933a0c84a47bc70237f6","tid":2131850,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"全日禁堂食措施昨（29日）開始生效，各處均可見市民於戶外狼狽用膳。有見及此，社會上不少有心人為一眾打工仔提供免費用饍的地方，尖沙咀的髮型屋Hair La Forme亦免費為市民開放午膳空間直至晚上六時，並為每人送上十個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n負責人盧小姐表示，政府把關不力，昨日港人隨街吃飯的照片令她感到心酸，所以她希望盡一分力，騰出空間讓港人可以「食啖安樂茶飯」。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指，明天會恢復午市堂食，但盧小姐表示髮型屋會一直開放，直到政府放寬防疫措施為止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHgV5EJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHgV5EJ.jpg&h=8299e05d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPo5Jrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPo5Jrp.jpg&h=fc4702ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gi5zBMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGi5zBMq.jpg&h=bdc3d0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwJA5EL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwJA5EL.jpg&h=069e5d06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afxiiZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafxiiZM.jpg&h=9bb3b3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1221666294843444/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1221666294843444%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=90b6486c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1221666294843444/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3c50a1c07a6be22830bf22500018ff1aa2983afa","tid":2131850,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/